# Storybook

## Story File Conventions
- Every component must have a corresponding `.stories.tsx` file inside its folder
- Use `satisfies Meta<typeof Component>` for type-safe meta
- Always include `tags: ["autodocs"]` for automatic documentation
- Set `parameters.layout` to `"centered"` for isolated components or `"padded"` for layout components

## Story Structure
- Export a `default` meta object with `title`, `component`, `parameters`, `tags`, and `argTypes`
- Export individual stories as named `StoryObj` constants
- Include at minimum: one story per variant, one disabled state, and one "AllVariants" composition story

## ArgTypes
- Define `control` type for each prop (`"select"`, `"boolean"`, `"text"`)
- Include a `description` for every argType

## Decorators
- The `AtlasProvider` is already applied globally via `.storybook/preview.tsx`
- Do not wrap individual stories with `AtlasProvider`
